\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26a1c77ec731c95993e6aed9243df1c2097d1d43","tid":1192093,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"呢個係民陣既呼籲<br />\n請在場人士切勿衝擊及佔領立法會<br />\n違者將被檢控！"},{"pid":"3b2452d2e293ecf272b82061269644dceec18393","tid":1192093,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0bcf133eab1b1dd5fcf03297faaa5e1ba73ba5fb","tid":1192093,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"整個Trump save HK  Banner囉"},{"pid":"b5822eb256ebe81e3baba2a4357f7c2713d62442","tid":1192093,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2964fb562719c5e40769834e2e45e8b85ec94413","tid":1192093,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:39:54.000Z","msg